    <header class="hero-section">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-copy">
                <span class="eyebrow">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
                <h1>More revenue. Less uncertainty.</h1>
                <p>We turn marketing investment into a stable flow of qualified contacts so you can grow with predictability every month.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="#final-cta" class="btn btn-primary">Get Audit</a>
                    <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">See Real Results</a>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-trust" aria-label="Trust indicators">
                    <span><i aria-hidden="true">✓</i>+50 companies helped</span>
                    <span><i aria-hidden="true">↗</i>Average ROI 4.2x</span>
                    <span><i aria-hidden="true">◷</i>Weekly reports</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-visual">
                <div class="visual-card">
                    <div class="visual-topbar">
                        <span class="visual-tag">Sica Growth Panel</span>
                        <span class="visual-live">Updated now</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="visual-screen">
                        <div class="visual-chart-card">
                            <div class="visual-chart-header">
                                <p>Qualified Leads (30 days)</p>
                                <strong class="countup" data-target="37" data-prefix="+" data-suffix="%">+37%</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div class="visual-chart-grid" aria-hidden="true">
                                <span></span>
                                <span></span>
                                <span></span>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <svg class="visual-chart" viewBox="0 0 360 170" role="img" aria-label="Lead growth chart">
                                <defs>
                                    <linearGradient id="chartStroke" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                                        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#b7d356" />
                                        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#6f5aa3" />
                                    </linearGradient>
                                </defs>
                                <polyline points="0,145 38,130 76,122 114,110 152,96 190,86 228,70 266,64 304,49 342,32" />
                            </svg>
                            <div class="visual-metrics">
                                <article class="visual-metric-card">
                                    <strong class="countup" data-target="37" data-prefix="+" data-suffix="%">+37%</strong>
                                    <span>Leads</span>
                                </article>
                                <article class="visual-metric-card">
                                    <strong class="countup" data-target="-22" data-suffix="%">-22%</strong>
                                    <span>CAC</span>
                                </article>
                                <article class="visual-metric-card">
                                    <strong class="countup" data-target="4.2" data-suffix="x" data-decimals="1">4.2x</strong>
                                    <span>ROAS</span>
                                </article>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="visual-kpis">
                            <article class="visual-kpi">
                                <span>Budgets this week</span>
                                <strong class="countup" data-target="128">128</strong>
                            </article>
                            <article class="visual-kpi">
                                <span>Cost per lead</span>
                                <strong class="countup" data-target="14.2" data-prefix="€" data-decimals="2">€14.20</strong>
                            </article>
                            <article class="visual-kpi">
                                <span>Conversion rate</span>
                                <strong class="countup" data-target="11.6" data-suffix="%" data-decimals="1">11.6%</strong>
                            </article>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="problem-awareness" class="section section-problem">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <span class="section-label">The Problem</span>
                    <h2>Busy every day<br>but your business isn't growing?</h2>
                    <p class="problem-intro">If your schedule is full but revenue isn't scaling predictably, the problem isn't effort. It's lack of system.</p>
                    <div class="problem-points">
                        <div class="problem-point">
                            <div class="problem-point-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M2 10 C4 6,6 12,8 8 C10 4,12 7,14 5" stroke="#6F5AA3" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Inconsistent leads</strong>
                                <p>Good months followed by slow weeks, with no predictability over the volume of qualified contacts.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="problem-point">
                            <div class="problem-point-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6" stroke="#6F5AA3" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="M8 5v3.5M8 11h.01" stroke="#6F5AA3" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>High activity, low results</strong>
                                <p>Scattered campaigns, dispersed investment and decisions by intuition instead of actionable data.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="problem-point">
                            <div class="problem-point-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="9" width="2.5" height="5" rx="1" fill="#6F5AA3"/><rect x="6.5" y="6" width="2.5" height="8" rx="1" fill="#6F5AA3" opacity="0.55"/><rect x="11" y="3" width="2.5" height="11" rx="1" fill="#6F5AA3" opacity="0.3"/></svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Uncontrolled growth</strong>
                                <p>You don't know what works, how much each customer costs, or where you're losing margin.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="comparison" class="section section-copy">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-label">Strategic Clarity</span>
                    <h2>Traditional marketing vs performance-driven method</h2>
                    <p>The difference between executing isolated actions and building an acquisition engine with control, predictability and scale.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="comparison-cards">
                    <div class="comparison-card comparison-card--dark">
                        <h3>Traditional Marketing</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Inconsistent leads and unstable schedule</li>
                            <li>Focus on vanity metrics</li>
                            <li>Decisions without actionable data</li>
                            <li>Investment without predictable return</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="comparison-card comparison-card--light">
                        <h3>Sica Method</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Continuous flow of qualified contacts</li>
                            <li>Focus on revenue and margin</li>
                            <li>Performance monitored in real-time</li>
                            <li>Clear and scalable ROI</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="case-studies" class="section section-case-studies">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-label">Case Studies</span>
                    <h2>Real proof of performance, not promises</h2>
                    <p>Projects where we connected investment to measurable growth with direct impact on revenue.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="studies-grid">
                    <article class="study-card">
                        <h3>+75% qualified leads</h3>
                        <p>Paid structure for premium clinic with increased appointments and continuous drop in cost per lead.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="study-card">
                        <h3>+120% organic traffic</h3>
                        <p>SEO plan driven by commercial intent that doubled visibility and consolidated recurring demand.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="study-card">
                        <h3>2x conversions in funnel</h3>
                        <p>Reengineering of landing pages and creatives to multiply quote requests with the same traffic.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

