        <section id="blog" class="section section-blog">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-label">Performance Insights</span>
                    <h2>Better decisions create faster growth</h2>
                    <p>Practical content to increase acquisition efficiency, improve conversion and scale with consistency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="blog-grid">
                    <article class="blog-card">
                        <div class="blog-thumb">
                            <img src="assets/ferramentas/google-business-thumbnail.jpg" alt="Google Business profile with local presence metrics" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <h3>How to reduce CPA by 30%</h3>
                        <p>Segmentation, creatives and account structure to reduce acquisition cost without losing volume.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="blog-card">
                        <div class="blog-thumb">
                            <img src="assets/blog/seo-google-search-console.jpg" alt="Specialist analyzing Google Search Console on MacBook" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Local SEO to capture nearby customers</h3>
                        <p>Objective steps to dominate local searches and generate contacts with higher purchase intent.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="blog-card">
                        <div class="blog-thumb">
                            <img src="assets/ferramentas/wordpress-speed-booster-thumbnail.jpg" alt="Performance dashboard for conversion optimization" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Landing pages that sell more</h3>
                        <p>Critical elements of copy, proof and UX to increase conversion without increasing investment.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="faq" class="section section-faq">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
                    <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header">How long does it take to see results?</button>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <p>In paid traffic campaigns, results start appearing within days. For SEO, we expect significant gains in 3 to 6 months.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header">Can I start without images or ready-made branding?</button>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <p>Yes. The strategy and media plan can be delivered with text and positioning. Images can be added later without impacting launch.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header">What's the minimum investment to get started?</button>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <p>The initial investment depends on the sector, but our campaigns start with a lean monthly budget, adjusted to your growth objective.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact-form" class="section section-contact-form">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="section-label">Contact us</span>
                    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
                    <p>Share your goals and receive a clear growth plan in the next 24 hours.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-form-wrapper">
                    <form class="contact-form" id="contactForm">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="subject">Subject</label>
                            <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group form-group--full">
                            <label for="message">Message</label>
                            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
